        <title>Claude Notch</title>
        <item>
            <title>0.3.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Polish and clarity</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Clearer credits tile</b>: the subline now shows this month's extra-usage spend in absolute money ("€45.21 of €50.00/mo") instead of a bare percent, so an emptied balance can't look like leftover headroom</li>
                    <li><b>New "Refresh now"</b> in the right-click menu refetches the selected provider immediately</li>
                    <li>Smoother under the hood: log discovery moved off the main thread (no UI stalls with large histories), a rare file-watcher race fixed, and stable chart bar identities</li>
                    <li>VoiceOver: the expand control, page dots, and sessions toggle are now proper labeled buttons</li>
                    <li>Building from source auto-detects your Xcode toolchain</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 14:34:58 +0200</pubDate>
