        <item>
            <title>0.3.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Claude & Codex</h2>
                <p>The island now tracks <b>two providers</b>. Click the left icon (or use the right-click Provider menu) to switch between Claude and Codex. Codex support was contributed by <a href="https://github.com/0xhyperdan">@0xhyperdan</a>.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Codex</b>: rate-limit windows with reset countdowns, account token totals, credits, and recent tasks, all via the official local codex app-server (ChatGPT or Codex app, Homebrew, or PATH)</li>
                    <li><b>Week at a glance</b>: both providers chart the last 7 days in the island — Claude's local spend in dollars, Codex's account tokens, with today highlighted and the peak day labeled</li>
                    <li><b>Credits balance</b>: the Claude credits tile shows your purchased usage-credit balance with the monthly spend as subline</li>
                    <li>Cleaner pages: all-time joined the limits page, and empty filler tiles are gone</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Privacy unchanged: everything stays local, talking only to the respective first-party services with your own sessions. Thanks to <b>0xhyperdan</b> for the contribution.</p>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 13:19:53 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.3.0</sparkle:version>
