        <item>
            <title>0.2.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Usage-credit balance on the credits tile</h2>
                <p>The credits tile now shows your purchased <b>usage-credit balance</b> (the "Current balance" figure from claude.ai's Usage credits settings), with this month's extra-usage spend as the subline.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Accounts with usage credits enabled but nothing spent now read "0% used" instead of "none"</li>
                    <li>The balance is fetched with your existing session; if it can't be read, your limit tiles are unaffected</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 10:20:17 +0200</pubDate>
