        <item>
            <title>0.1.9</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Hide in full screen</h2>
                <p>New right-click menu toggle <b>Hide in full screen</b> (off by default). When it's on, the island tucks up into the notch while a full-screen app owns that display — great for movies and full-screen video — and slides back down when you leave full screen.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Opt-in, so nothing changes unless you enable it</li>
                    <li>Reliable on notched Macs, where a full-screen window otherwise looks just like a maximized one</li>
                    <li>Permission-free detection — no Accessibility prompt</li>
                    <li>Smooth slide-up / slide-down transition</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Resolves issue #2.</p>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 00:20:09 +0200</pubDate>
